            // Wizard Stepper Section
            section.py-5.bg-light
            .container.px-5.my-5
                .text-center.mb-5
                h2.fw-bolder Our Process
                p.lead.fw-normal.text-muted Transform Your Business in 5 Simple Steps

                .d-flex.justify-content-between.flex-wrap.position-relative.stepper
                // Step 1
                .step.completed.text-center.flex-fill.position-relative
                    .step-indicator 1
                    .step-label.mt-2 Take a look
                    p Explore the range of plans we offer below to find the one that best suits your needs.

                // Step 2
                .step.completed.text-center.flex-fill.position-relative
                    .step-indicator 2
                    .step-label.mt-2 Free Consultation
                    p Drop us an email, let us know how we can help. We will talk you through your options and what we will deliver.

                // Step 3
                .step.completed.text-center.flex-fill.position-relative
                    .step-indicator 3
                    .step-label.mt-2 The Build
                    p We’ll hold a series of sessions throughout your website build to guide the process. Our iterative development approach allows us to adapt quickly and effectively to any changes along the way.

                // Step 4
                .step.completed.text-center.flex-fill.position-relative
                    .step-indicator 4
                    .step-label.mt-2 The Review
                    p You'll have dedicated time to review everything agreed upon during our consultation. This is your opportunity to request any final changes before your project goes live.


                // Step 5
                .step.completed.text-center.flex-fill.position-relative
                    .step-indicator 5
                    .step-label.mt-2 The Go-Live
                    p The exciting part — Go Live! Once we’ve finalized everything and you’re happy with the result, we’ll launch your website and take it live.


